items.description:
This LyCORIS has been trained after carefully selecting 57 images. All photos have been enhanced to make the most of them. I hope you like it!


I don't ask for anything but any respectful constructive review (after having tested the model) would be highly appreciated or at least press Like if you're happy with results after trying it out! Thanks in advance and enjoy it!

Alexandra Anna Daddario (born March 16, 1986) is an American actress. She had her breakthrough portraying Annabeth Chase in the Percy Jackson film series (2010–2013). She has since starred as Paige in Hall Pass (2011), Heather Miller in Texas Chainsaw 3D (2013), Blake Gaines in San Andreas (2015), Summer Quinn in Baywatch (2017), and Alexis Butler in We Summon the Darkness (2019). She has also guest starred in television series such as White Collar, It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia, True Detective, New Girl, and American Horror Story: Hotel. In 2021, she starred in the first season of the HBO series The White Lotus, for which she received widespread critical acclaim and an Emmy nomination for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Limited or Anthology Series or Movie in 2022. In 2023 she began playing the lead role of Dr. Rowan Fielding in the AMC show Mayfair Witches based on a series of novels written by author Anne Rice.

items.name: Yae Miko (Genshin Impact) Cosplayer - Amateur
items.description:
Introduce

Anonymous amateur cosplayer plays as Yao Miko (Genshin Impact)

Limitation

  • You can't generate NSFW images from this model.

  • Commercial use of this model is strictly forbidden.

Usage

I've trained this model in 1125 steps of 5 epochs. Because all images have very similar backgrounds and costumes, I uploaded the model of third epochs for the best mixing custom backgrounds or clothes.

Even in weight 1.0 it still works on changing backgrounds and clothes; I still recommend you can try use lower weight such as 0.7.

This model was trained based on majicMixRealistic_v6 and I guess you still can use it on the other big model.

The trigger words you can use are 1girl, cosplay, yae miko.

I strongly recommend you use this model with DDSD, adetailer and controlnet for the best result.

items.name: Miss Fortune | League of Legends
items.description:
LoRA trained on Miss Fortune from League of Legends

requested by: pretty much everyone

I tried to make her default skin as consistent as possible since the others focused more on the lore MF. However, you can still create the lore MF

I didn't include Captain MF in this LoRA because it would have overbled into everything else and made the captain hat and outfit mix with her default one. I really wanted to avoid that because my goal was to make default MF as consistent as possible without pruning, which would make it less flexible. However, I have the dataset ready for Captain MF, so it will also be uploaded today or tomorrow :)

default: miss fortune \(league of legends\), 1girl, pirate hat, bra, strap slip, bare shoulders, detached sleeves, wide sleeves, pants

lore mf: miss fortune \(league of legends\), 1girl, bare shoulders, off shoulder, cleavage, pants

anime: Kawaii Realistic Anime Mix - A0.2, YabaL_Mix - V5, Cetus-Mix

2,5D: Aniverse - Aniverse V1.1, Dark Sushi 2.5D, MeinaUnreal - V4.1, DarkSun - v4.0

realistic: Paragon V1.0, Kawaii Realistic European Mix - v0.3, OnlyAnime

negative embeddings: Fast Negative Embedding v2

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned (for realistic models & 2,5D), kl-f8-anime2, blessed2.vae (for anime models)

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras or DPM++ 2M Karras(euler a for img2img upscaling) from time to time im also using DPM++ 2M alt Karras

  • Steps: 20 to 35

  • Clipskip: 2

  • Upscaler : GitHub - pkuliyi2015/multidiffusion-upscaler-for-automatic1111 4x-UltraSharp(for 2,5D & realistic), 4xAnimesharp(for anime)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9 (mostly 7)

  • LORA weight for txt2img: 0.5-1 (for the examples i mostly used 0.8 and 1)

  • Denoise strength upscaling: 0.3 to 0.55

If you want to autocomplete the tags & trigger im using, I recommend using Booru style tag autocompletion for AUTOMATIC1111's Stable Diffusion web UI

For full body shots i recommend using: ComfyUI Impact Pack

or the a1111 alternative GitHub - Bing-su/adetailer

items.name: Milly Alcock (JG)
items.description:
Milly Alcock is an Australian actress, mainly known for her role as the younger version of Rhaenyra Targaryen in the HBO series House of the Dragon.

I've made a few changes for this TI. Namely, I've used 4 vectors per token instead of 2 (a previous try with just 2 had produced less than ideal results, although I think the initial dataset was at fault). I've also used a final dataset of 13 images, which is less than usual. The step I'm uploading is 130, by the way.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Building a good prompt with my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (m4lc0ck:0.99), a woman as a movie star, modelshoot style, (extremely detailed CG unity 8k wallpaper), photo of the most beautiful artwork in the world, professional majestic oil painting by Ed Blinkey, Atey Ghailan, Studio Ghibli, by Jeremy Mann, Greg Manchess, Antonio Moro, trending on ArtStation, trending on CGSociety, Intricate, High Detail, Sharp focus, dramatic, photorealistic painting art by midjourney and greg rutkowski, (white turtleneck top:1.2), ((movie premiere)), (long skirt), ((standing near a movie theater)), ((paparazzi in the background)), (looking at viewer:1.2), (detailed pupils:1.3), ((closeup portrait:1.1))"

items.name: tutu's HiSilk(8D White Glossy Over-the-Knee Socks)/ 图图的嗨丝（8D白色油亮长筒袜）/チュチュのハイシー（8D白色のオイル光沢長い膝上靴下）
items.description:
感谢：丢了猫のBOY；落月；reluxion；帮忙测试LORA~

交流Q群：882894837，欢迎来玩，互通有无。

简介：

这是一个白丝LORA，可以改善图中白丝的质感。

厚度：8D

颜色：black

类型：油亮长筒过膝袜

不要被这个LORA如此小的体积所迷惑！

本LORA的特点如下：

1、使用差异提取法精心制作，所以体积很小。除了会对丝袜的质感产生影响以外，对画面的其他内容影响较小。

2、全部采用真人照片高清相机拍摄制作，确保效果真实。

3、因为对画面其他内容影响较小，即使权重开的很大也没有关系。

为什么已经有了这么多白丝LORA，还要再做一个？因为我发现：

items.name: Westmix V.0, Photo Realistic Model for Beautiful Western Girl
items.description:
Model Updated, Westmix V1.0 Official Version:

https://civitai.com/models/117463/westmix-v1-photo-realistic-model-for-beautiful-western-girl

1. Motive:

So, like, for a while, I got totally bored with the whole table diffusion thing and didn't bother making any models or pulling images at all. (Actually there was some issue with Youtube back then. lol). But recently, I got bored outta my mind, so I started again. I was sick of all the photo realistic models I made before, so I just messed around with other people's models for fun. But even though Civitai's photo realistic models of Western girls are really awesome, there were a few things that bothered me, so I decided to suck it up and quickly make one myself for fun.

The common issues I found with these Western girl-related photo realistic models here are:

1. The background details aren't clear enough.

2. They're tagged as photo realistic, but in reality, they're more like semi-photo realistic.

3. If the prompt gets even a bit long, the model just doesn't apply it properly.

4. If the realism is too high, the overall image clarity takes a serious hit.

5. When I try to generate Western girl images, they often end up looking quite far from the actual Western girls' features.

6. When taking a full body shot, if the composition is way off, and there are too many specific prompts, the model just ignores them. As a result, the face gets messed up, or the whole thing ends up lacking any realism at all. (even with detailer extension)

2. About Sample Images:

To work on improving these aspects bit by bit, I uploaded a basic model, even though it's a bit unstable. I know it will be a long way to go, but, at least, IT'S NOT BORING! I'm planning to keep updating it to achieve better quality in the future.

None of the sample images I uploaded have been edited at all. And, I didn't even pick the ones that turned out well; I just uploaded whatever was generated. This means there are some images with odd hands.

Most of the sample photos have their exif info out in the open, but the highest quality ones didn't bother sharing it. Even for those images without exif, I generated them without using any Lora (except for only one noise related) or anything. The only difference is that I did some technical tweaks using my own know-how. Please Figure out how to technically increase the sense of photo realism and quality by yourself just with the model (not loras and embeddings). It's another fun and I don't want to take it away from you. :)

*I see so many unnecessarily overweighed multiple '()' in the neg. prompt of some low, middle quality sample images as well as missing commas. Just make them with only one parenthesis when you feel your prompts are ignored. And, put ',' on the missing spots. I was sleepy...so... Sorry!

3. About Prompts and Extensions:

1. My negative prompts are recommended if you are a nub. Otherwise, just play with them and find better combinations. BUT DO NOT OMIT "((Asian))" in Neg. Prompt.!!

2. Try various positive prompts. They get applied well in a proper setting and will change the image quality entirely depending on how good they are.

3. DDetailer and Dynamic Threshold are recommended depending on your compositions...etc.

4. Things to Work on More:

I'm quite satisfied with all except for the photo realism of face part. I will work more on that and some minor stuff for the next official version, v1

5. About NSFW:

I am not interested in NSFW at all. Never tested or done anything for that. So, I have no idea how my model does on NSFW.

Alrite~ Let's begin the f@#$%$# journey!

items.name: MixTape /// Blues
items.description:
Both image and music are windows to the deepest feelings, inviting us to explore the nuances of life through its different forms of expression.

Let's create a gallery full of inspiration! Post your masterpieces and let's fill civitai with imagination, creativity, expression and joy!

The Model MixTape Blus is similar to the MixTape Rock n' Roll, using the model DuckHaitenNiji in its base, but with a different mix. It's not very good with your hands, but it creates images with rich details and colors.

The Delta version is the most stylized. It creates very colorful images, with lots of detail and a more three-dimensional finish.

The Swamp version has more realistic proportions but still creates stylized, colorful and very detailed images. Features more facial expressions and more varied backgrounds.

Recommends

Positive Prompt:

(masterpiece, best quality:1.4), (beautiful, perfect, delicate, detailed, intricate, aesthetic:1.2), ...

Negative Prompt:

EasyNegative, BadHands, BadArtist, BadArtistAnime, BadPrompt, (low quality, worst quality:1.4), (monochrome, grayscale, sketch:1.2), (logo, signature, text, words, username, artist name, watermark), (loli:1.2), ...

Embeddings (Textual Inversion): EasyNegative, BadHands, BadArtist, BadArtistAnime, BadPrompt

Sampling method: DPM++ SDE Karras

Sampling steps: 30 ~ 50

Hires. fix:

Sampler: 4x-UltraSharp

Hires steps: 6 ~ 10

Denoising strength: 0.5

Upscale by: 2 (resize from 512x768 to 1024x1536)

Clip skip: 2

CFG Scale: 7 ~ 8

VAE: kl-f8-anime2 VAE

Merge Recipe

Merged models are the following:

  • DucHaitenNiji

  • OS-GoldenHarvest

  • FantasticChix-HR

Delta Steps:

  1. Base = GoldenHarvest x 0.7 + FantasticChixHR x 0.7

  2. Delta = Base x 0.3 + DucHaitenNiji x 0.7

Swamp Steps:

  1. Base = GoldenHarvest x 0.7 + FantasticChixHR x 0.7

  2. Delta = Base x 0.5 + DucHaitenNiji x 0.5

License

All used models here have "Have different permissions when sharing merges" license permission, so I do not try to add any restriction on it.

Bath Time!!

This Lora is designed to recreate bathing in a bathtub. I've never been impressed with bathing recreations straight out of the box for stable diffusion, so this aims to fix it. As always, I's using my own custom model for all of these generated images which can be found HERE, but I've confirmed it works well on other models, and even anime style models. Let me know what you think!!!

items.name: 边缘弱化/强化 Edge weaken/strengthen エッジ弱化/強化
items.description:
这个rola模型可以增强或减轻甚至融合画面的边缘：

权重设置为正值使边缘更模糊，可以达到类似柔化、权重加大时甚至会出现类似水粉画、油画的效果。

权重设置为负值让边缘更清晰，有使线条变得流畅、圆滑的效果，可以使远处的人物都变得清晰；

因为每个checkpoint模型画风不太相同，所以没有固定适合的权重，推荐值-2~+2；

用法1：采用正权重时有轻微的隐藏效果：人物整体更容易被背景色浸染。推荐和细节加强lora同时使用，推荐放大算法为latent，可使画面色彩更为丰富，使画面富有艺术感。

用法2：采用负权重，让边缘更清晰但不会使线条变得很粗，可以让远处的人物更为清晰，详见图例中的女孩子人群（超大的景深是我的背景控制lora造成的）。同时在使用tile放大图片时，可以减轻重绘造成的图像崩坏。

用法3：用于真实模型时，设置正权重时发挥类似柔光的效果，对色调偏暗的大模型有一定改善效果。

This rola model can enhance or reduce or even fuse the edges of the image:

When the weight is set to a positive value, the edge become blurred, which can achieve the effect similar to softening, or even similar to Gouache painting and oil painting when the weight is increased.

Setting the weight to a negative value makes the edges clearer and making the lines smoother. It can also make characters in the distance clearer;

Due to the different styles of each checkpoint model, there is no fixed suitable weight. Normally a recommended value is -2 to+2;

Usage 1: When using positive weights, there is a slight hidden effect: the overall character is more likely to be stained by the background color. Recommend using Lora together with add_detail. The recommended magnification method is latent, which can make the image more colorful and artistic.

Usage 2: Using negative weights to make the edges clearer, but this lora won't make the lines too thick and make the distant characters clearer. Please refer to the crowd of girls in the legend for details. (The large depth of field is caused by my background control Lora).

At the same time,it can reduce the image collapse caused by redrawing, when using <tile> to enlarge an image,

Usage 3: When using a realistic model, setting positive weights would produces a soft light like effect, which has a certain improvement effect on checkpoint models with darker tones.

このrolaモデルは、画面のエッジを強化、または軽減、融合したりすることができます。

ウェイト値を正の値に設定し、エッジをぼかすと、ソフト化に類似した効果が発揮します。ウェイトをさらにアップした時に、水粉画、油絵のような効果が現れることもあります。

ウェイト値を負の値に設定することでエッジが鮮明になり、線が滑らかになる効果があり、遠くの人物もはっきりさせることができます。

checkpointモデルごとに画風が異なるため、適切なウェイト値が固定されません。しかしながら、普通の場合推奨値-2 ~+2、

使用法1：正の重みを使用した場合にわずかな隠れ効果がある：人物全体が背景色に染まりやすい。推薦には、add_detailのloraを同時に使用。推薦の拡大方法はlatentで、画面の色を更に豊富にすることができて、画面を芸術感に富ませることができます。

使用法2：負の重みを設定する時、エッジをより鮮明にしますが、線を太くすることはありません。遠くの人物をもっとはっきりさせることができて、詳しくは凡例の女の子の人混みを参照してください。（巨大な被写界深度は私の背景制御loraによるもの）。また、tileを使用して画像を拡大する場合、再描画による画像の崩壊を軽減することができます。

使用法3：写真類のモデルに使用する場合、正の重みを設定する際に柔らかい光のような効果を発揮し、色調が暗いなcheckpoint モデルに対して一定の改善効果がある。
